Enhances: ${xpi:Enhances}
Description: adds icons to Iceweasel's  URL, search and find input fields to clear their contents.
 This add-on places an X-icon at the end of the URL, search and quickfind field
 to clear these fields.
 .
 This is useful for X-windows users who don't want their clipboards to be erased
 when marking the text in the field to delete it.
